data.description: This Johnsburg 2 story has 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths.  Perfect layout for entertaining.  The entry and first floor dining and family room all have oak hardwood floors.  The finished, freshly painted basement can be massive game room or extra bedroom.  The rear deck overlooks garden, mature landscaping, large rear yard with playsets. Attached gas grill on deck included!  Primary Bedroom features walk in closet and private bathroom. Large laundry/mudroom area with room for freezer/beer fridge. Wood burning fire place in family room. Attached, heated garage has floored loft for storage and easy access to hot/cold water already in rear wall. Newer upgrades include HVAC with humidifier/electronic air filter, on demand water heater, garage heater, garage door, kitchen fridge and mircrowave.  Seller did most upgrades within the last year. Prefer weekend showings or evenings.  Great location with Johnsburg schools!
